    "Table II shows the performance report for LLM-based assertion generation.",
    "The first column, \"Module\" shows different designs we have taken.",
    "The third column, \"LLM Assert.",
    "\", shows the number of SV assertions generated by LLM for each design, and the second column, \"OT Assert.",
    "\", shows the number of assertions provided in the RTL of OpenTitan."
